#: lib/extensions/wbc_importer/extension_wbc_importer.php:269
msgid ""
"This demo content importer has been built to make the import process as easy "
"for you as possible. We&#39;ve done what we can to ensure as little "
"difficulty as possible. We have also gone the extra mile to add in the extra "
"things are sorted for you, such as setting the home page, menu, and widgets -"
" things that aren&#39;t possible with the standard WordPress Importer!</br>"
"</br>\n"
"                    <strong>Steps to take before using this plugin:</strong>"
"</br></br>\n"
"\n"
"    1. The import process will work best on a clean install. You can use a "
"plugin such as WordPress Reset to clear your data for you.</br>\n"
"    2. Ensure all plugins are installed beforehand, e.g. WooCommerce - any "
"plugins that you add content to.</br>\n"
"    3. Once you start the process, please leave it running and uninteruppted."
"</br>\n"
"    4. Enjoy</br>"
msgstr ""

